snippet.title: The Rip | Official Teaser | Netflix
snippet.description:
Upon discovering millions in cash in a derelict stash house, trust among a team of Miami cops begins to fray. As outside forces learn about the size of the seizure, everything is called into question — including who they can rely on. Starring Matt Damon and Ben Affleck & Directed by Joe Carnahan, The Rip is only on Netflix, January 16.

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81915745

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

The Rip | Official Teaser | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

snippet.title: The FUNNIEST MOMENTS In Steal A Brainrot..
snippet.description:
Today I reacted to the funniest steal a brainrot video ever. Make sure you watch the whole video to find out what happens.

Merch: https://foltyn.shop/

Join this channel to get access to perks:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCRkuUgtDAL4XSU5jB40J_wA/join

--Socials--

Discord: https://discord.gg/hqwZhrkqRr

Roblox Group: https://www.roblox.com/groups/11775558/Foltyns-Family#!/about

Roblox Name: TheRealFoltyn

Insta: https://www.instagram.com/realfoltyn/

Twitter: https://twitter.com/Foltynnn

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

#Roblox #foltyn

snippet.title: Borderlands 4 - Official Cinematic Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
► Buy Borderlands 4 Now: https://2kgam.es/Borderlands4

Watch as Vex, Rafa, Amon, and Harlowe take on the Timekeeper in the Official Cinematic Launch Trailer for Borderlands 4 - available TODAY on PlayStation®5, Xbox Series X|S, PC via Steam and the Epic Games Store! 💥 Borderlands 4 launches on Nintendo Switch 2 on October 3, 2025.

--------------------------------------------

Borderlands 4 is a mayhem-fueled looter shooter, jam-packed with billions of weapons, outrageous enemies, and intense co-op action. Explore a dangerous hidden planet Kairos as one of four new badass Vault Hunters.

Break free from the oppressive Timekeeper, a ruthless dictator who dominates the masses from on high. Now, a world-altering catastrophe threatens his perfect Order, unleashing mayhem across the planet. Ignite a resistance and blast your way through mechanical monstrosities, bloodthirsty bandits, and vicious beasts, with new traversal mechanics like: double jumping, gliding, dodging, fixed-point grappling, and more.

Fight solo or in co-op with up to three other players in this immense sci-fi adventure, packed with free-form combat and exploration, pulse-pounding boss fights, infinitely varied loot drops, and an eclectic cast of unforgettable characters new and old.

--------------------------------------------

snippet.title: Gorillaz - The Happy Dictator ft. Sparks (Official Visualiser)
snippet.description:
Gorillaz - The Happy Dictator ft. Sparks (Official Visualiser)

The Mountain, new album out 20th March.

Listen to The Happy Dictator: https://gorillaz.ffm.to/thehappydictator
Pre-order the album: https://gorillaz.ffm.to/themountain

Subscribe to Gorillaz https://gorillaz.os.fan/signup

Shop Gorillaz: https://store.gorillaz.com/

Lyrics: 
I am the one to give you life again 
I am the one to save your soul, AMEN!

As the shadows they are forming come and join me centre stage

Oh what a happy land we live in

If you are empty and abstracted and your broken heart is full of rage

Oh what a happy land, oh yeah

In a world of fiction I am a velvet glove 

Oh what a happy land we live in

I am your soul, your resurrection, I am the love

Oh what a happy land, oh yeah

So look out to the west now, see where the devil lies

Oh what a happy land we live in


It’s pharmakon is with you and your empire it is paralysed 

Oh what a happy land, oh yeah

I’ll propagate eternity and seal it with my kiss

Oh what a happy land we live in

So look into the coffin and let me grant your wish

Oh what a happy land, oh yeah
 
No more bad news 
So you can sleep well at night 
And the palace of your mind will be bright

Everything is slowing down yet everything is faster

Oh what a happy land we live in

While everyone is consuming I’ll save you from yourself

Oh what a happy land, oh yeah
 
Upon this world of fiction my love I will bestow

Oh what a happy land we live in

And as we march into the future happiness will grow

No more bad news 
So you can sleep well at night
And the palace of your mind will be bright

Everything is slowing down yet faster 
Consuming us I’ll save you from yourself
My love bestowed upon this world of fiction
March to the future happiness grows
Are you not better off than ever 
Are you not better off right now
When have you felt this way I ask you
When have you felt better off than right now

I am the one to give you life again
I am the one to save your soul, AMEN!

No more bad news………

(Mountains and rainbows , palaces of love)

So you can sleep well at night and palace of your mind will be bright

So you can sleep well at night and palace of your mind will be bright

#themountain #gorillaz #newmusic #kong

snippet.title: Charlie
snippet.description:
for all of the bile
the bold talk
the venom
the hate and the lies
no one should be killed
no blood should be spilled
Charlie shouldn't have died

well you can't hate the gun and love the gun that shot yer rival
you can't be kind and wish pain upon a child
everybody's gotta say
what they're needing to say
as soon as they're needing to say it
the freedom to speak
to be a freak
and the freedom to say you hate it
and have a big ole conversation

I heard laughing
I heard glee
but it coulda been you
it coulda been me

out in the bloodshed everyone loses
there's unforgettable scars
out in the bloodshed permanent bruises
shapes up who you are
children left to wander america aimless
with a firebrand of resent
wondering who it is took my daddy
with a destiny of revenge
out in the bloodshed the cycle begins
and everyone dies
spin the wheel, if you don't get killed
you wind up dead inside

I heard laughing
I heard glee
but it coulda been you
it coulda been me

snippet.title: Minecraft LIVE Official Trailer – September 2025
snippet.description:
Minecraft LIVE is the show to watch if you want to learn that latest news from the world of Minecraft. The next Minecraft LIVE will be broadcast on September 27 at 7PM CEST/10AM PDT.

We’ll feature the inside scoop on unannounced game drops, insight from our developers, and more!
After the broadcast, stay tuned in for the Deep Dig After Show where our developers and guests show off the new features, often resulting in chaos. Vu Bui will return as host and attempt to keep things running smoothly. Good luck to that guy!

See you there! September 27 ! Watch it at https://www.minecraft.net, YouTube, Twitch, Instagram or TikTok.

snippet.title: Borderlands 4 Review
snippet.description:
Borderlands 4 reviewed by Travis Northup on PC. Also available on PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series X/S.

"Borderlands 4 is a badass open-world evolution of a wonderfully unhinged looter-shooter series that needed to try something new, and it largely nails the biggest swings it takes. Combat is slicker than ever thanks to exciting new movement options and some interesting enemy designs, and the entertaining story takes things in a fresh direction while still tying neatly into existing lore. The transition to an open world isn’t the smoothest, especially when troubling terrain with a few too many invisible walls can make it feel like these environments are all for show, but that’s more than worth putting up with in exchange for being able to chart your own path and freely explore the wacky, violent world of Kairos. The bugs my crew and I encountered were bad enough to occasionally sour our co-op groove, but in between them we had a great time, and my friends and I have found ourselves utterly at the mercy of its loot grind. The Borderlands series feels like it has been a bit stuck in the mud for some time now, and especially after a few patches, Borderlands 4 is exactly the kick in the pants it has needed."

내 영향력을 잃어가고 있어, 내가 사기꾼이 아니라는 모든 증거들
다시 내 머릿속에 너무 깊이 빠져들어, 아무리 세게 두드려도 아무도 들여보내지 않아

그리고 그들의 메아리는 뼈로 만든 감옥에 홀로 앉아 있어
오, 싫어, 하지만 내 집이야

필요하다면 날 놓아줘도 괜찮아

머물 거야?
내가 절대 변하지 않고, 빌린 시간 동안 모두를 밀어낸다면 나에 대해 뭐라고 말할까?
보답할 수 없어?

의미 있는 삶에 안주하려 애썼지만, 길을 잃고 싶어
그리고 그걸 끊으려 애썼지, 박수 소리에 절벽으로 걸어갔지
그리고 그 메아리는 뼈로 만든 감옥에 홀로 앉아 있어
오, 싫어, 하지만 내 집이야

어디서든 나는 긴장해, 하지만 여전히 내가 강요하는 것 같아
필요하면 날 놓아줘도 괜찮아

잠이 들 때 너 없이 도망가는데, 네 머릿속에선 항상

IMPOSE // गीत

मैं अपना प्रभाव खो रहा हूँ, सारे सबूत कि मैं सिर्फ़ धोखेबाज़ नहीं हूँ
फिर से मेरे दिमाग़ में बहुत गहराई तक, किसी को भी अंदर नहीं आने दूँगा, चाहे वे कितनी भी ज़ोर से दस्तक दें

और उनकी गूँज हड्डियों से बनी जेल में अकेली बैठी है

हर जगह मैं चौकन्ना रहता हूँ, और फिर भी मुझे लगता है कि मैं थोप रहा हूँ
अगर तुम्हें ज़रूरत हो तो मुझे जाने देना ठीक है

अगर मैं सोते समय तुम्हारे बिना भाग जाऊँ और तुम्हारे दिमाग़ में मैं हमेशा
रहने वाला हूँ, तो यह मेरे बारे में क्या कहेगा?
अगर मैं कभी नहीं बदलूँ और सबको उधार के समय में दूर धकेल दूँ, तो यह मेरे बारे में क्या कहेगा?
मैं चुका नहीं सकता?

मैंने एक प्रासंगिक जीवन में बसने की कोशिश की, लेकिन मैं खो जाना चाहता हूँ।
और मैंने इसे तोड़ने की कोशिश की, तालियों की गड़गड़ाहट के साथ खाई की ओर चला गया।
और उनकी गूँज हड्डियों से बनी एक जेल में अकेली बैठी है।
ओह, मुझे इससे नफ़रत है, लेकिन यह मेरे लिए घर है।

हर जगह मैं चौकन्ना रहता हूँ, और फिर भी मुझे लगता है कि मैं थोप रहा हूँ।
अगर तुम्हें ज़रूरत हो तो मुझे जाने देना ठीक है।

IMPOSE // 歌詞

俺は自分の影響力を失っている。俺がただの詐欺師ではないという証拠はすべて
またしても頭の中の奥深くに深く入り込み、どんなに強く叩かれても誰も入れない

そして、彼らの残響は骨でできた牢獄にぽつんと座っている
ああ、嫌だ、でもここが俺の家なんだ
どこにいても俺は気を張り詰めている、それでも俺は邪魔をしているような気がする
俺を手放してもいいもし必要なら

眠りに落ちて、君と離れて逃げ出したとしても、君の頭の中ではずっと
ここにいるつもりだとしたら、それは僕について何を意味するんだろう？
もし僕が決して変わらず、借り物の時間で皆を遠ざけてしまうとしても、それは僕について何を意味するんだろう？
返済できないの？

私は意義のある人生に落ち着こうとしたけれど、迷子になりたくてたまらない。
そしてそれを断ち切ろうとした。拍手の音の中、崖っぷちまで歩いた。
そして拍手の反響は骨でできた牢獄の中で、ただ一人佇んでいる。
ああ、嫌だ、でもそこが僕にとっての故郷なんだ。

どこにいても僕は気を張り詰めているけれど、それでも僕は邪魔をしているように感じる。
もし必要なら、僕を手放してもいいよ。

眠りに落ちて、君と離れて逃げ出したとしても、君の頭の中ではずっと
ここにいるつもりだとしたら、それは僕について何を意味するんだろう？
もし僕が決して変わらず、借り物の時間で皆を遠ざけてしまうとしても、それは僕について何を意味するんだろう？
返済できないの？

Ich verliere meinen Einfluss, alle Beweise dafür, dass ich kein Hochstapler bin.
Wieder zu tief in meinem Kopf, lasse niemanden rein, egal wie hart sie zuschlagen.

Und ihre Echos sitzen allein in einem Gefängnis aus Knochen.
Oh, ich hasse es, aber es ist mein Zuhause.
Überall bin ich auf Zack, und trotzdem habe ich das Gefühl, mich aufzudrängen.
Es ist okay, mich gehen zu lassen, wenn du es brauchst.

ich kann es nicht zurückzahlen?

Und ihre Echos sitzen allein in einem Gefängnis aus Knochen.

Überall bin ich auf Trab und habe trotzdem das Gefühl, mich aufzudrängen.
Es ist okay, mich gehen zu lassen, wenn du es brauchst.

Was sagt es über mich aus, wenn ich ohne dich weglaufe, wenn ich einschlafe und in deinem Kopf immer bleiben werde?

Was sagt es über mich aus, wenn ich mich nie ändere und alle auf geborgter Zeit von mir stoße, weißt du, dass ich es nicht zurückzahlen kann?

snippet.title: The Sims 4 Adventure Awaits | Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Pre-order The Sims™ 4 Adventure Awaits Expansion Pack*, available Oct 2: https://www.ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/buy/addon/the-sims-4-adventure-awaits-expansion-pack Order now through Nov 13 for the Warm & Cozy Digital Content**; the Toasty Tower Lamp, Toast-Tea Kettle, and Toasty Tootsies Socks.

Start your adventure: https://www.ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/news/adventure-awaits-expansion-pack

Want to see more Sul Sul Island? Follow The Sims social channels for more adventures!

Get ready to break free from the everyday with daring activities and Getaways. Getaways are more than vacations, they are experiences you design! Set a schedule and even add rules. Elimination Rules – like skill or relationship gains – will have Sims competing to outlast each other. Create a kids’ camp, fitness retreat, romantic contest, or anything else you can imagine!

Also, create Custom Venues, where you can design, build and decorate, deciding what kinds of activities and roles are assigned. Share your creation to the Gallery for other Simmers to download and us for their own Getaways!

Live a more adventurous life with new skills: Entomology, Diving, Archery and Papercrafts. Make classic crafts like paper planes, catch and raise butterflies, make a splash with new diving boards, and hit the bullseye! These activities are for both kids and grown-ups, as are the Diving Board, Waterslide, and Kayak. Get out there and explore the water! Active Adult Sims will enjoy working out with Spin Bikes and Free Weights, and everyone will enjoy drinking a refreshing smoothie from the new Blender.

snippet.title: Season 4 Battle Pass: Fruit of Immortality | Official Trailer | Marvel Rivals
snippet.description:
A new season dawns, rooted in legend and eternal life. The Season 4 Battle Pass Fruit of Immortality awaits those who dare to claim it, available to purchase starting September 12 UTC.

This Battle Pass holds 10 costumes and exclusive cosmetics, including free rewards like Captain America's Golden Age and Magneto's The Trial Of Magneto costumes. Upgrade to unlock even more treasures hidden within the immortal fruit.

From the sacred peaks of K'un-Lun to the Immortal Dragon soaring through the skies, uncover the mystery of the enchanted branch and its fruit - a symbol of peace, protection, and boundless life.

Take the branch, embrace its power, and fight for eternity in Season 4: The Heart of Dragon! ✨

Play free now on:
🔹 Steam: https://t.co/IPhy0Of1cG
🔹 PlayStation: https://t.co/FR0aVfTmcn

snippet.title: Yandel - Nunca Me Olvides (Letra)
snippet.description:
🎵 Yandel - Nunca Me Olvides (Letra)
📸 Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/ted_sad_
🔔 Activate notifications to find out about new videos!

👉 Follow

› Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/yandel/?hl=es-la

 .........

🐻 TED CARS:
➥ Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/ted_sad_/
➥ Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/TEDSADagain/

🎤 Letra: Nunca Me Olvides

[Intro]
Nah-ah, nah (Uoh-oh-oh-oh)
Dangerous
Nah-ah, nah-ah (Eh, eh, eh)
Nah-ah, nah
Nah-ah, nah-ah (Eh-eh, eh-eh-eh)

[Pre-Coro]
Fantasma eres tú cuando andas por ahí (Oh)
Ni me reconoces de frente a ti (Eh, eh-eh; oh)
Y anoche estuve yo mirando tus fotos
Quisiera que me digas si piensa en nosotros (¡Suelta!)
Llevo ya mucho tiempo buscando una aventura (Plah)
Quiero que me regales un viaje por tu cintura (Oh-oh, oh, oh)

[Coro]
(Oh, oh, oh)
Quiero tu cuerpo (Oh, oh; heh-heh)
Dame tus labios (Oh, oh, oh)
Pero nunca me olvides (Eh-eh)
Si el destino te cambió
Quiero tu cuerpo (Pah, pah)
Dame tus labios
Pero nunca me olvides (Ouh)
Si el destino te cambió (Heh, heh)

[Verso 1]
Aún recuerdo cómo tú besas (Muah)
Me volvías loco de la cabeza (Jajajajaja)
Dime qué te cuesta darme una respuesta
Si yo sé que al igual que yo tú a mí me piensas (¡Plah!)
Siempre detrás de ti yo estoy
Y si tú me llamas, rápido voy
No hay ninguna así como tú ma'i (Heh, heh)
Dime si tú ma'i te vas conmigo hoy (¡Suelta!)

[Refrán]
Y si dices que no (¡Duro!), yo te convenzo
No hay ninguna así como tú ma'i (Pah, pah, pah, pah, pah)
Dime si tú ma'i te vas conmigo hoy (¿Qué, qué?)

[Pre-Coro]
Llevo ya mucho tiempo (¡Yandel!)
Buscando una aventura (¡Dangerous!)
Quiero que me regales un viaje por tu cintura (Uoh, oh, oh, oh)

[Coro]
(Oh, oh, oh)
Quiero tu cuerpo (Eh-eh-eh; oh, oh, oh)
Dame tus labios (Oh, oh, oh)
Pero nunca me olvides (Eh-eh)
Si el destino te cambió (Ajá)
Quiero tu cuerpo
Dame tus labios
Pero nunca me olvides
Si el destino te cambió

[Verso 2]
Cuánto deseo que en mí pienses (Pah)
Y regreses a mis brazos donde puedo tenerte (¿Qué, qué?)
Y abrazarte, y decirte (Heh, heh)
Que más nunca yo quisiera perderte
Y si aceptas mi invitación, yo te espero en mi habitación
Para darte sexo y pasión (Pah)
Tú eres tentación (Pah)
Conmigo la pasas mejor (¡Yandel!)

[Refrán]
Y si dices que no (¡Yandel!), yo te convenzo
No hay ninguna así como tú, ma'i
Dime si tú mai', te vas conmigo hoy
(Oye, bebé, nunca me olvides)

[Pre-Coro]
Fantasma eres tú cuando andas por ahí
Ni me reconoces de frente a ti (¿Cómo?; jajajajajaja)
Y anoche estuve yo mirando tus fotos (¡Yandel!)
Quisiera que me digas si piensa en nosotros
Llevo ya mucho tiempo buscando una aventura (¡Duro, duro, duro!)
Quiero que me regales un viaje por tu cintura (¡Rrah!)

[Coro]
(Oh, oh, oh)
Quiero tu cuerpo (Oh, oh)
Dame tus labios (Oh, oh, oh)
Pero nunca me olvides (Eh-eh)
Si el destino te cambió (¡Suelta!)
Quiero tu cuerpo (Eh, eh)
Dame tus labios (¡Dangerous!)
Pero nunca me olvides
Si el destino te cambió

[Outro]
Sólo te pido que no me olvides
Yandel "La Leyenda Viviente"
Y Entertainment
EARCANDY
Jumbo "El Que Produce Solo"
El poderío
Jajajajaja
Otra liga, sonando refrescante
Sonido único

snippet.title: Avengers: Doomsday (2026) - First Trailer | Marvel
snippet.description:
#avengers #avengersdoomsday #robertdowneyjr 

The Avengers will assemble one last time. 

Editing, VFX, SFX, Thumbnail by @KHStudio please subscribe:
✅ YouTube: https://bit.ly/KHstudio

🎥 Attention viewers!

Please note that this video is a concept trailer created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes. I have meticulously incorporated various effects, sound design, AI technologies (Google Veo 3), movie analytics, and other elements to bring my vision to life. Its purpose is purely artistic, aiming to entertain and engage with the YouTube community. My goal is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through this trailer. Thank you for your support, and let's dive into the world of imagination! 🍿

🦸‍♂  Avengers: Doomsday

Logan, now an iconic film in the superhero genre, marked Hugh Jackman's farewell as Wolverine. But what if the story didn't end there? That's the question posed by this new video, and as you can see above, it's primarily a heartfelt tribute to Jackman. The Australian actor, once an unknown, took on the role of the X-Men character, portraying him multiple times over a 17-year span.

While Logan served as the perfect conclusion for the hero, depicting a man worn down by years of war and violence, the trailer hints at a potential resurrection for him. It emphasizes his enduring need for family and his desire to reintegrate into the X-Men world.

Regarding Logan specifically, while there's widespread enthusiasm to witness Hugh Jackman in a potential Logan 2, it's hard to surpass the excellence of the original film. It fulfilled the long-awaited desire for an R-rated Wolverine movie, a feat many thought unlikely given the rating and tone.

Now, with this new fan trailer in view, do you find your eagerness for a Logan sequel reignited, or is it merely a skillfully crafted homage to Jackman's performance? 

Feel free to express your thoughts on this exciting project by leaving a comment below.

snippet.title: CHAINSAW MAN – THE MOVIE: REZE ARC | Dub Trailer | Crunchyroll
snippet.description:
Everyone’s after his chainsaw heart.

For the first time, see Chainsaw Man - The Movie: Reze Arc exclusively in movie theatres October 24. Watch the trailer now. #ChainsawManMovie

For the first time, Chainsaw Man slashes his way onto the big screen in an epic, action-fueled adventure that continues the hugely popular anime series. Denji worked as a Devil Hunter for the yakuza, trying to pay off the debt he inherited from his parents, until the yakuza betrayed him and had him killed. As he was losing consciousness, Denji’s beloved chainsaw-powered devil-dog, Pochita, made a deal with Denji and saved his life. This fused the two together, creating the unstoppable Chainsaw Man. Now, in a brutal war between devils, hunters, and secret enemies, a mysterious girl named Reze has stepped into his world, and Denji faces his deadliest battle yet, fueled by love in a world where survival knows no rules.

Directed by: Tatsuya Yoshihara 
 
Based on the original work “Chainsaw Man” by Tatsuki Fujimoto (Serialized in Shueisha’s “Shonen Jump+”)

Screenplay by: Hiroshi Seko 

Production by: MAPPA 

© 2025 MAPPA/CHAINSAW MAN PROJECT ©Tatsuki Fujimoto/SHUEISHA

Credits not final

Wildcard gets explosive with a new Mythic Flatline and new Wild Card abilities to help you make things go boom. Mad Maggie and Seer updates blow up the scene, plus an opportunity to get new Legendary Skins and the new Fuse-inspired Mythic Flatline.

エイリアン・アース エピソード7予告編のイースターエッグを網羅。『ジュラシック・パーク』への言及、エイリアンの標本の脱走、島に逃げ込んだゼノモーフ、モローのチーム。エイリアン・アース エピソード6 ザ・フライ エンディング、エイリアン映画への言及、ザ・フライ映画、プレデター・バッドランズ映画、エイリアン1979、ジェームズ・キャメロン監督のエイリアン、エイリアン映画のタイムライン、ゼノモーフ種族の説明、エイリアン・アースのタイムラインと登場人物。2種類の新しいゼノモーフ。モローのバックストーリー。そして空飛ぶエイリアンの標本。エイリアン・アース エピソード7 予告編。

エイリアン映画の撮影中に地球で何が起こったか。タイムラインの初期に地球に現れたエイリアン・ゼノモーフ。エイリアン・ロミュラスとその続編への言及、リプリーのエイリアンへの言及、プロメテウスのイースターエッグ、エンジニア。ウェイランド・ユタニ社、プロディジー社、シンセvsハイブリッド。

エイリアン・アースは、ノア・ホーリーがエイリアンシリーズを原作に制作したアメリカのSFホラーテレビシリーズです。 1979年公開のオリジナル映画『エイリアン』の2年前、2120年を舞台にした前日譚です。シドニー・チャンドラー、アレックス・ロウザー、エッシー・デイヴィス、サミュエル・ブレンキン、バブー・シーセイ、アダルシュ・グラヴ、ティモシー・オリファントが出演します。

マーベルの予告編が続々公開！『アベンジャーズ5』ドゥームズデイ予告編、『サンダーボルト』予告編、『アベンジャーズ6』シークレット・ウォーズ予告編、そして『スパイダーマン：ブラン・ニュー・デイ』予告編も！

『エイリアン・アース』第7話の完全版動画は来週火曜の夜に公開！『ピースメーカー』シーズン2第4話の動画は木曜に投稿！

에일리언 어스 7화 예고편 등장 이스터 에그. 쥬라기 공원 관련 내용, 외계 생명체 탈출, 섬에 풀려난 제노모프, 모로우의 팀. 에일리언 어스 6화 플라이 엔딩, 에일리언 영화 관련 내용, 플라이 무비, 프레데터 배드랜즈 영화, 1979년 에일리언, 제임스 카메론 감독의 에일리언, 에일리언 영화 타임라인, 제노모프 종족 설명, 에일리언 어스 타임라인 및 등장인물. 두 가지 새로운 제노모프 생명체. 모로우의 배경 이야기. 그리고 날아다니는 에일리언 표본. 에일리언 어스 7화 예고편

에일리언 영화 속 지구에서 일어나는 일들. 타임라인 초반에 지구에 나타난 에일리언 제노모프. 에일리언 로물루스와 후속작 참조, 리플리 에일리언 참조, 프로메테우스 이스터 에그, 엔지니어들. 웨이랜드 유타니 코퍼레이션, 프로디지 코퍼레이션, 신스 vs. 하이브리드.

에일리언 어스는 노아 홀리가 제작한 미국의 SF 공포 TV 시리즈로, 에일리언 시리즈를 기반으로 합니다. 1979년 원작 영화 에일리언보다 2년 앞선 2120년을 배경으로 한 프리퀄입니다. 시드니 챈들러, 알렉스 로터, 에시 데이비스, 새뮤얼 블렌킨, 바부 시세이, 아다르쉬 구라브, 티모시 올리펀트가 출연합니다.

더 많은 마블 예고편이 곧 공개됩니다! 어벤져스 5 둠즈데이 예고편, 썬더볼츠 예고편, 어벤져스 6 시크릿 워즈 예고편, 스파이더맨 브랜드 뉴 데이 예고편 영상!

एलियन अर्थ एपिसोड 7 के ट्रेलर में ईस्टर एग्स के उभरने की झलक। जुरासिक पार्क के संदर्भ, एलियन नमूनों का पलायन, द्वीप पर ज़ेनोमोर्फ का खुला होना, मॉरो की टीम। एलियन अर्थ एपिसोड 6 का द फ्लाई एंडिंग, एलियन फिल्मों के संदर्भ, द फ्लाई फिल्म, प्रिडेटर बैडलैंड्स फिल्में, 1979 का एलियन, जेम्स कैमरून के एलियन, एलियन फिल्म की समयरेखा, ज़ेनोमोर्फ जाति की व्याख्या, एलियन अर्थ की समयरेखा और पात्र। 2 नए ज़ेनोमोर्फ जीव। मॉरो की पिछली कहानी। और उड़ता हुआ एलियन नमूना। एलियन अर्थ एपिसोड 7 का ट्रेलर।

एलियन फिल्मों के दौरान पृथ्वी पर क्या होता है। समयरेखा में पहले पृथ्वी पर एलियन ज़ेनोमोर्फ। एलियन रोमुलस और सीक्वल संदर्भ, रिप्ले एलियन संदर्भ, प्रोमेथियस ईस्टर एग्स, द इंजीनियर्स। वेयलैंड युटानी कॉर्पोरेशन, प्रोडिजी कॉर्पोरेशन, सिंथ्स बनाम हाइब्रिड्स।

एलियन अर्थ, नोआ हॉले द्वारा निर्मित एक अमेरिकी विज्ञान-कथा हॉरर टेलीविजन श्रृंखला है, जो एलियन फ्रैंचाइज़ी पर आधारित है। यह 1979 की मूल फिल्म एलियन की घटनाओं से दो साल पहले, 2120 में सेट एक प्रीक्वल के रूप में कार्य करती है। इसमें सिडनी चैंडलर, एलेक्स लॉथर, एस्सी डेविस, सैमुअल ब्लेंकिन, बाबू सीसे, आदर्श गौरव और टिमोथी ओलीफेंट मुख्य भूमिका में हैं।

जल्द ही और भी कई मार्वल ट्रेलर आएंगे: एवेंजर्स 5 डूम्सडे ट्रेलर, थंडरबोल्ट्स ट्रेलर, एवेंजर्स 6 सीक्रेट वॉर्स ट्रेलर और स्पाइडर-मैन ब्रैंड न्यू डे ट्रेलर वीडियो!

मेरा पूरा एलियन अर्थ एपिसोड 7 का वीडियो अगले मंगलवार रात को पोस्ट होगा! मेरा पीसमेकर सीज़न 2 एपिसोड 4 का वीडियो गुरुवार को पोस्ट होगा!

Over Alien Earth Aflevering 7 Trailer: Emergence Easter Eggs. Verwijzingen naar Jurassic Park, Ontsnapping van buitenaardse wezens, Xenomorph losgelaten op het eiland, Morrows team. Alien Earth Aflevering 6: The Fly Einde, Verwijzingen naar Alien-films, The Fly-film, Predator Badlands-films, Alien 1979, James Cameron Aliens, Alien-filmtijdlijn, Xenomorph-ras uitgelegd, Alien Earth-tijdlijn en personages. De 2 nieuwe Xenomorph-wezens. Morrows achtergrondverhaal. En het Flying Alien Specimen. Trailer van Alien Earth aflevering 7.

Wat er op aarde gebeurt tijdens de Alien-films. Alien Xenomorph op aarde eerder in de tijdlijn. Referenties aan Alien Romulus en sequels, verwijzingen naar Ripley Alien, Prometheus Easter Eggs, The Engineers. Weyland Yutani Corporation, Prodigy Corporation, Synth's vs Hybrids.

Alien Earth is een Amerikaanse sciencefiction-horrorserie, gemaakt door Noah Hawley, gebaseerd op de Alien-franchise. Het is een prequel die zich afspeelt in 2120, twee jaar voor de gebeurtenissen in de originele film Alien uit 1979. De hoofdrollen worden gespeeld door Sydney Chandler, Alex Lawther, Essie Davis, Samuel Blenkin, Babou Ceesay, Adarsh ​​Gourav en Timothy Olyphant.

Binnenkort nog veel meer Marvel-trailers: Avengers 5 Doomsday-trailer, Thunderbolts-trailer, Avengers 6 Secret Wars-trailer en Spider-Man gloednieuwe Day-trailervideo's!

Alien Earth, Odcinek 1 – Finał Odcinka 8 https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLOIeYdZ3QczzNwEARuHxVretci623PP2b

Omówienie easter eggów ze zwiastuna 7. odcinka Alien Earth. Nawiązania do Parku Jurajskiego, ucieczki obcych, ksenomorfów na wyspie i zespołu Morrowa. Alien Earth, odcinek 6: Zakończenie "Mucha", Nawiązania do filmów o Obcym, Film "Mucha", Filmy "Predator: Badlands", Obcy 1979, Obcy Jamesa Camerona, Chronologia filmu "Obcy", Wyjaśnienie rasy ksenomorfów, Chronologia i postacie z "Obcego" z "Obcego". Dwa nowe ksenomorfy. Historia Morrowa. I latający okaz obcego. Zwiastun 7. odcinka "Obcego".

Co dzieje się na Ziemi w filmach o Obcym? Obcy ksenomorf na Ziemi we wcześniejszej części linii czasowej. Nawiązania do "Obcego" Romulusa i sequeli, Nawiązania do "Obcego" Ripley, Easter Eggs z "Prometeusza", Inżynierowie. Weyland Yutani Corporation, Prodigy Corporation, Synth kontra hybrydy.

Alien Earth to amerykański serial science fiction z gatunku horror stworzony przez Noaha Hawleya, oparty na serii "Obcy". Film stanowi prequel, którego akcja rozgrywa się w roku 2120, dwa lata przed wydarzeniami z oryginalnego filmu „Obcy” z 1979 roku. W rolach głównych występują Sydney Chandler, Alex Lawther, Essie Davis, Samuel Blenkin, Babou Ceesay, Adarsh ​​Gourav i Timothy Olyphant.

Wkrótce więcej zwiastunów Marvela: zwiastun Avengers 5 Doomsday, zwiastun Thunderbolts, zwiastun Avengers 6 Secret Wars i zwiastun Spider-Man Brand New Day!

Mój PEŁNY film z 7. odcinka „Obcy: Ziemia” zostanie opublikowany we wtorek wieczorem! Mój film z 4. odcinka 2. sezonu „Peacemaker” zostanie opublikowany w czwartek!

snippet.title: Borderlands 4 Review - It’s NOT What We Thought? Performance, Gameplay, Endgame & More
snippet.description:
Borderlands 4 is finally here, and after 150+ hours of gameplay we’ve put together our full review and impressions. Thank you 2K games for providing the early review copy! From the new Vault Hunters and expanded skill trees to the loot chase, endgame systems and performance updates, Borderlands 4 is both bigger and more refined than we expected. In this video we’ll break down the story, gameplay, co-op experience, loot, builds and whether it’s worth your time if you’re a Borderlands fan or new to the series.

00:00 Borderlands 4 Review
00:40 What Is Borderlands 4?  
01:16 The Story  
02:13 The World & Map  
04:01 The Combat & Gameplay  
07:10 The Loot  
09:17 The Endgame  
10:59 The Performance & Graphics  
13:01 Steam Deck  
13:41 Final Thoughts

snippet.title: Saja Boys (Kpop Demon Hunters) 'Your Idol' (Color Coded Lyrics)
snippet.description:
Thank you so much for watching the video! 🙌 Don't forget to like and subscribe ♡

• Artist: SAJA BOYS
• Song ♫: 'YOUR IDOL'
• Album: KPOP DEMON HUNTERS

🎵Lyrics🎵
[Intro]
Pray for me now
Pray for me now (Dies irae)
Pray for me now (Illa)
Pray for me now (Vos solve in)
Pray for me now (Favilla)
Pray for me now (Maledictus)
Pray for me now (Erus)
Pray for me now (In flamas)
Pray for me now (Aeternum)
I'll be your idol

[Verse 1: Abby, Romance, Mystery, Mystery & Abby]
Keeping you in check (Uh), keeping you obsessed (Uh)
Play me on repeat, kkeudeobsi in your head
Anytime it hurts (Uh), play another verse (Uh)
I can be your sanctuary
Know I'm the only one right now (Now)
I will love you more when it all burns down
More than power, more than gold (Yeah)
Yeah, you gave me your hеart, now I'm here for your soul

[Pre-Chorus: Jinu]
I'm the only onе who'll love your sins
Feel the way my voice gets underneath your skin

[Chorus: Jinu, Abby]
Listen 'cause I'm preachin' to the choir
Can I get the mic' a little higher?
Gimme your desire
I can be the star you rely on (You rely on)
Nae hwanghol-ui chwihae, you can't look away (Hey)
Don't you know I'm here to save you?
Now we runnin' wild
Yeah, I'm all you need, I'ma be your idol

[Post-Chorus]
Uh
Uh

[Verse 2: Baby, Abby, Romance]
Uh! bichi naneun fame, gyesok oechyeo, I'm your idol
Thank you for the pain 'cause it got me going viral
Uh, yeah, natji anneun fever, makin' you a believer
Nareul wihae neon jonjaehaneun idol
Don't let it show, keep it all inside
The pain and the shame, keep it outta sight
Your obsession feeds our connection
I sungan give me all your attention

[Pre-Chorus: Jinu]
You know I'm the only one who'll love your sins
Feel the way my voice gets underneath your skin

[Chorus: Jinu, Romance]
Listen 'cause I'm preachin' to the choir
Can I get the mic a little higher?
Gimme your desire
I can be the star you rely on (You rely on)
Nae hwanghol-ui chwihae, you can't look away (Yeah)
Don't you know I'm here to save you?
Now we runnin' wild
Yeah, I'm all you need, I'ma be your idol

[Post-Chorus: All]
Be your idol

[Bridge: All, Jinu]
Living in your mind now
Too late 'cause you're mine now
I will make you free
When you're all part of me

[Chorus: Jinu, All]
(Listen 'cause I'm) Preaching to the choir
(Now) Can I get the mic a little higher?
Gimme your desire
Watch me set your world on fire
Nae hwanghol-ui chwihae, you can't look away (Hey)
No one is coming to save you
Now we runnin' wild
You're down on your knees, I'ma be your idol

snippet.description:
Mammoth: "I Really Wanna" (Official Video)

THE NEW ALBUM:
Mammoth - The End out 10/24/25
Pre-Order Mammoth's new album "The End" today here:  https://Mammoth.lnk.to/TheEndAlbum

ON TOUR:
Check out The End Tour here: https://mammoth.band

Dec 3 – Denver, CO – Ogden Theatre
Dec 6 – Tempe, AZ – Marquee Theatre
Dec 7 – Anaheim, CA - House Of Blues


GRAMMY® Award-nominated songwriter, vocalist, multi-instrumentalist, and producer Wolfgang Van Halen continues to separate Mammoth from the pack. The music stands alone on a foundation anchored by his impressive sonic proficiency (across drums, bass, keys, and guitar) and airtight arena-size hooks with unforgettable vocals. He harbors an irresistible signature sound, inventive vision, and incomparable identity vaunted by a fervent global fanbase. For as unique as the music is, his story so far proves to be just as unprecedented. This is arguably the first hard rock act to genuinely break out from ground zero in the 2020’s, generating north of 100 million streams, toppling charts, and selling out headline tours less than five years since its debut. Back in 2021, Mammoth’s first offering, Mammoth WVH, took flight, bowing at #12 on the Billboard 200 and capturing #1 on three Billboard charts—Top Hard Rock Albums, Top Independent Albums, and Top Rock Albums. “Distance” soared as the first of two #1 Rock Radio Hits and earned a GRAMMY® Award nomination for “Best Rock Song.” Two years later, Mammoth II only saw him pick up the pace. It debuted in the Top 5 of the Billboard Top Album Sales Chart in addition to bringing him back to #1 on the Top Hard Rock Albums Chart. It incited widespread applause from Rolling Stone, Guitar World, GRAMMY.com, Classic Rock, American Songwriter, and KERRANG! The band canvased the globe with Metallica and Pantera and supported Foo Fighters in North America as well as filling houses on their own. They performed on ABC’s Jimmy Kimmel LIVE!, at MusiCares 2024 gala in honor of Jon Bon Jovi, and Wolf took the stage at the Rock and Roll Hall of Fame® Induction of Ozzy Osbourne. Now, Wolfgang pushes forward on Mammoth’s third full-length LP.

Connect with Mammoth at:
Website: www.mammoth.band
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/MammothWVH
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/mammothwvh/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/MammothWVH
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/@Mammoth

#Mammoth #WVH #MammothWVH #wolfgangvanhalen

GRAMMY® Award-nominated songwriter, vocalist, multi-instrumentalist, and producer Wolfgang Van Halen continues to separate Mammoth from the pack. The music stands alone on a foundation anchored by his impressive sonic proficiency (across drums, bass, keys, and guitar) and airtight arena-size hooks with unforgettable vocals. He harbors an irresistible signature sound, inventive vision, and incomparable identity vaunted by a fervent global fanbase. For as unique as the music is, his story so far proves to be just as unprecedented. This is arguably the first hard rock act to genuinely break out from ground zero in the 2020’s, generating north of 100 million streams, toppling charts, and selling out headline tours less than five years since its debut. Back in 2021, Mammoth’s first offering, Mammoth WVH, took flight, bowing at #12 on the Billboard 200 and capturing #1 on three Billboard charts—Top Hard Rock Albums, Top Independent Albums, and Top Rock Albums. “Distance” soared as the first of two #1 Rock Radio Hits and earned a GRAMMY® Award nomination for “Best Rock Song.” Two years later, Mammoth II only saw him pick up the pace. It debuted in the Top 5 of the Billboard Top Album Sales Chart in addition to bringing him back to #1 on the Top Hard Rock Albums Chart. It incited widespread applause from Rolling Stone, Guitar World, GRAMMY.com, Classic Rock, American Songwriter, and KERRANG! The band canvased the globe with Metallica and Pantera and supported Foo Fighters in North America as well as filling houses on their own. They performed on ABC’s Jimmy Kimmel LIVE!, at MusiCares 2024 gala in honor of Jon Bon Jovi, and Wolf took the stage at the Rock and Roll Hall of Fame® Induction of Ozzy Osbourne. Now, Wolfgang pushes forward on Mammoth’s third full-length LP.

snippet.title: Beéle - si te pillara (Letra/Lyrics)
snippet.description:
Beéle - si te pillara (Letra/Lyrics)

Follow Beéle:
https://www.instagram.com/beele
https://www.tiktok.com/@beele
https://www.facebook.com/beelemusica

🎤 Letra / Lyrics: Beéle - si te pillara

[Intro]
Pilla, hay ojos que no se hacen los ciegos
Porque las paredes no solo tienen oídos, ¿Oiste?
También tienen bemba

[Verso 1]
Siento que pronto me fallarás
Yo digo: “ver para creer”
Muchos me dicen que ya hay alguien más que te vieron por ahí con un tal “Estás loco marico. Ve a terapia”

[Pre-coro]
Te siento distante, un poco arrogante, ya siento que no sentimos lo de antes, aunque yo de tu boca no sentimos nada
Si te pillo con el gyal, si te pillara…

[Coro]
Ay, ay, ay, si te pillara
Si te pillara, ay si te pillara
Si te pillara, ay si te pillara
Si te pillo los ojitos se me aguarán
Que alguien más te toque eso me asara, si tus labios pillo con otros, lloro

[Verso 2]
Si me mientes devuelve mi cora destrozado
Eso no aguanta esto me hace sentir desconfiado
Las ganas de verte a mi lado
Las digo en pasado
Perdí las esperanzas porque siento que me haces a un lado
Y sisaya pero cayaya, tu haciendo lo tuyo y yo aquí en la playa
Recuerdo tu boddy cuando guaya yeh me da nostalgia
Te extraño tanto ya no te siento
Duele tu decisión de dejarme en la nada
Si esto es real como están diciendo…
Me moriría si yo te pillara

[Coro]
Y, ay, ay, si te pillara
Si te pillara, ay si te pillara
Si te pillara, ay si te pillara
Si te pillo los ojitos se me aguarán
Que alguien más te toque eso me asara, si tus labios pillo con otros lloro
Y, ay, ay, si te pillara
Si te pillara, ay si te pillara
Si te pillara, ay si te pillara
Si te pillo…

my lover's got humour
she's the giggle at a funeral
knows everybody's disapproval
i should've worshipped her sooner
if the heavens ever did speak
she's the last true mouthpiece
every sunday's gettin' more bleak
a fresh poison each week
we were born sick,
you heard them say it
my church offers no absolutes
she tells me,
"worship in the bedroom"
the only heaven i'll be sent to
is when i'm alone with you
i was born sick, but i love it
command me to be well
a, amen

take me to church
i'll worship like a dog
at the shrine of your lies
i'll tell you my sins
and you can sharpen your knife
offer me that deathless death
oh, good god, let
me give you my life

snippet.title: Beéle - top diesel (Letra)
snippet.description:
✨¡Muchas gracias por ver el video! espero que les haya gustado. ✨

🔔 Activa las notificaciones para enterarte de los nuevos vídeos!

📧Para promociones: latinflowpromotions@gmail.com

Muchas gracias por todo el apoyo, si te gusta el contenido que subo, no olvides suscribirte al canal y compartir los vídeos con tus amigos 

▶️ Primero mira el vídeo oficial por aquí:
https://youtu.be/8H61_9M6IUs?si=JZbdgWnWhdoDd2Dp

📝 Letra/ Lyrics:
Top diesel, top de cara, top princess
Pasa que dije algo que escuché en Capcana
Dice, Dice un bro: No te vayas a enamorar, 
yo me dije: Why, why
Se lo dije al corazón, no te vayas a enamorar
Y él se rie: “Ay, Ay”

Yo no sé decir que no, a no no no no nou
Yo no sé decir que no, a no no no no nou

Top diesel, top de cara, top princess
“Pero y ese afixie que tú tiene’ hermanito mío, sí viste esa tipa ahora mismo. ¿Why papa Dios?”

‘Toy viendo a la más linda
Le haría un hijo con ganas
Si así como baila, chinga
Vo’ a ser su playlist en la cama

Ella e’ la más linda
Por la noche a tu casa, quiero ir de visita
Parcharme a su mamá
Yo hago lo que toque, solo si me toca
Me imagino que esto suceda, desde que salió de mi boca
Dejo que me enamores
Me le pongo romanticón
Si mi tía me ve cachetón, diga “Carajo el amor engorda”
Yo no sabría decir que no
Quiero que sea su culpa
Que me ajuicie del borondo y me dé amorcito en pulpa
Hasta lo dijo mi cucha:

No te vayas a enamorar, yo me dije, Why why 
Se lo dije al corazón, no te vayas a enamorar
Y él se ríe “Ay, Ay”
Yo no sé decir que no, a no no no no nou


#Beéle #topdiesel
#Letra #LatinFlow

🎤 Lyrics: Meghan Trainor - Like I'm Gonna Lose You ft. John Legend

[Verse 1: Meghan Trainor]
I found myself dreamin' in silver and gold
Like a scene from a movie that every broken heart knows
We were walkin' on moonlight and you pulled me close
Split second and you disappeared and then I was all alone

[Pre-Chorus: Meghan Trainor]
I woke up in tears, with you by my side
A breath of relief, and I've realised
No, we're not promised tomorrow

[Chorus: Meghan Trainor]
So I'm gonna love you like I'm gonna lose you
I'm gonna hold you like I'm saying goodbye
Wherever we're standin', I won't take you for granted
'Cause we'll never know when, when we'll run out of time
So I'm gonna love you like I'm gonna lose you (Lose you)
I'm gonna love you like I'm gonna lose you

[Verse 2: John Legend, Meghan Trainor]
In the blink of an eye, just a whisper of smoke
You could lose everything, the truth is you never know
So I'll kiss you longer, babe (Hey), any chance that I get
I'll make the most of the minutes and love with no regret

[Pre-Chorus: John Legend, Meghan Trainor, Both]
Let's take our time to say what we want (Say what we want)
Use what we got before it's all gone (All gone)
'Cause no (No), we're not promised tomorrow

[Chorus: Meghan Trainor, John Legend, Both]
So I'm gonna love you like I'm gonna lose you (Lose you)
I'm gonna hold you (Hey), like I'm saying goodbye
Wherever we're standin' (Yeah), I won't take you for granted
'Cause we'll never know when, when we'll run out of time
So I'm gonna love you (I'm gonna love you), like I'm gonna lose you (Like I'm gonna lose you)
I'm gonna love you (Love you), like I'm gonna lose you (Hey)

[Instrumental Bridge]

[Chorus: Meghan Trainor, John Legend, Both]
I'm gonna love you (Oh) like I'm gonna lose you (Like I'm gonna lose you)
I'm gonna hold you like I'm saying goodbye
Wherever we're standin', I won't take you for granted
'Cause we'll never know when, when we'll run out of time
So I'm gonna love you (I'm gonna love you, baby) like I'm gonna lose you (Like I'm gonna lose you)
I'm gonna love you (Oh) like I'm gonna lose you

📧 Contact: mgmt.moonshine@gmail.com

snippet.title: I Played 30 Hours of Borderlands 4 (Review)
snippet.description:
After 30 hours with Borderlands 4, beyond some performance issues and at times poor pacing, I'm pleasantly surprised. Not what I expected.

00:00 Borderlands 4 Is Not What I Expected
01:08 Open World: POIs, Events, Bosses, Zones
09:55 Characters: Vex Is Life
11:42 Loot: There's Loads
14:52 Progressions: Levels, Skill Trees, SDU, Cosmetics
17:11 CONS: Performance, Pacing, Humor
22:25 PROS: Everything Else
24:06 Final Thoughts

snippet.title: I Tested a Brand New Slot Machine!
snippet.description:
I’m giving away $50,000 you DON’T want to miss it!: http://codebrettski.com 

We are BACK at the Casino… Playing a BRAND NEW slot machine! Let's see how this plays out, I'm expecting AT LEAST 3 hand-pays... if not 7. Thank you all so much for liking, subscribing, and dropping your thoughts in the comments. Even if you’re roasting me—I still love you. You’re all beautiful, and I truly appreciate every single one of you for riding along on this crazy journey.  Wish me luck, and I’ll see you in the next one! Let’s go to war.    

Brettski strode into the Neon Mirage Casino like a man with a mission—and $10,000 burning a hole in his pocket. The air buzzed with anticipation, lights flashing like sirens of fate. He wasn’t here for poker or roulette. No, tonight, he had eyes for one machine only: The Billionaire's Bounty, a brand-new slot machine rumored to have a glitch... one that could spill out the $1 billion jackpot.

He found it in the far corner, half-shrouded in shadow. No line, no fanfare—just a flickering screen and a strange hum, like it knew he was coming.

Brettski sat, fed in a crisp hundred, and pulled the lever.

Spin one: Cherry. Bar. Skull.
Spin two: Bar. Cherry. Skull.
Spin three: Skull. Skull. Skull.

The screen glitched—briefly flashing binary code—before returning to normal. The payout? $0.

He laughed it off, but noticed something weird: his watch was ticking backwards.

He kept playing. $100 after $100. Time itself seemed to blur—people moved slower, drinks stayed full, the air thicker. On spin 49, he hit three diamonds. The machine moaned and shot out a gold token.

“Insert to unlock Phase Two,” the screen whispered.

He hesitated. Then inserted it.

Suddenly, the machine split open, revealing a second screen… one that looked more like a satellite interface than a game. Coordinates flashed. Symbols in a language he didn’t recognize scrolled rapidly.

Security began approaching. Red lights flared. The machine spoke again:

“Jackpot authentication required. Place palm on scanner.”

Brettski reached out—then stopped. His palm had a strange mark, glowing faintly.

And then the casino floor began to rumble.

The screen flickered one final message:

“Only one player may claim the throne.”

And the floor gave out beneath him.

To be continued.

pl.title: Przetestowałem zupełnie nowy automat do gry!
pl.description:
Rozdaję 50 000 dolarów, których NIE CHCECIE przegapić!: http://codebrettski.com

WRÓCILIŚMY do kasyna… Grając na NOWYM automacie do gry! Zobaczymy, jak to się potoczy, spodziewam się PRZYNAJMNIEJ 3 wypłat… jeśli nie 7. Dziękuję wam wszystkim za polubienia, subskrypcje i dzielenie się swoimi przemyśleniami w komentarzach. Nawet jeśli mnie krytykujecie – nadal was kocham. Jesteście wszyscy piękni i naprawdę doceniam każdego z was za udział w tej szalonej podróży. Życzcie mi powodzenia i do zobaczenia w następnym! Chodźmy na wojnę.

Brettski wkroczył do kasyna Neon Mirage jak człowiek z misją – i 10 000 dolarów palących mu dziurę w kieszeni. Powietrze wibrowało od oczekiwania, światła migały jak syreny losu. Nie przyszedł tu po pokera ani ruletkę. Nie, dziś wieczorem miał oko tylko na jedną maszynę: The Billionaire's Bounty, zupełnie nowy automat do gry, o którym plotkowano, że ma usterkę... taką, która może wysypać jackpota wartego miliard dolarów.

Znalazł go w odległym kącie, na wpół spowity cieniem. Żadnej kolejki, żadnego rozgłosu – tylko migoczący ekran i dziwne buczenie, jakby wiedział, że nadchodzi.

Brettski usiadł, wrzucił świeżą stówkę i pociągnął za dźwignię.

Zakręć pierwszy: Wiśnia. Bar. Czaszka.
Zakręć drugi: Bar. Wiśnia. Czaszka.
Zakręć trzeci: Czaszka. Czaszka.

Ekran zaciął się – na krótko migał kod binarny – po czym wrócił do normy. Wypłata? 0 dolarów.

Zignorował to, ale zauważył coś dziwnego: jego zegarek tykał do tyłu.

Grał dalej. 100 dolarów po 100 dolarach. Sam czas zdawał się zacierać – ludzie poruszali się wolniej, drinki były pełne, a powietrze gęstniało. W 49. obrocie trafił trzy diamenty. Maszyna jęknęła i wyrzuciła złoty żeton.

„Włóż, aby odblokować fazę drugą” – wyszeptał ekran.

Zawahał się. Potem włożył żeton.

Nagle maszyna otworzyła się, odsłaniając drugi ekran… wyglądający bardziej jak interfejs satelitarny niż gra. Współrzędne zamigotały. Symbole w języku, którego nie znał, przewijały się szybko.

Ochrona zaczęła się zbliżać. Zapaliły się czerwone światła. Maszyna odezwała się ponownie:

„Wymagane uwierzytelnienie jackpota. Przyłóż dłoń do skanera”.

Brettski wyciągnął rękę – i znieruchomiał. Na jego dłoni był dziwny znak, słabo świecący.

A potem podłoga kasyna zaczęła drżeć.

Na ekranie pojawił się ostatni komunikat:

„Tylko jeden gracz może zasiąść na tronie”.

A podłoga pod nim zadrżała.

Ciąg dalszy nastąpi.

id.title: Saya Menguji Mesin Slot Baru!
id.description:
Saya akan membagikan $50.000 yang PASTI Anda tidak ingin melewatkannya!: http://codebrettski.com

Kami KEMBALI di Kasino… Memainkan mesin slot BARU! Mari kita lihat bagaimana hasilnya, saya mengharapkan PALING SEDIKIT 3 pembayaran langsung... kalau tidak 7. Terima kasih banyak atas like, subscribe, dan pendapat Anda di kolom komentar. Meskipun Anda mengejek saya—saya tetap menyayangi Anda. Kalian semua cantik, dan saya sangat menghargai setiap orang yang telah ikut serta dalam perjalanan gila ini. Doakan saya beruntung, dan sampai jumpa di putaran berikutnya! Ayo berperang.

Brettski melangkah masuk ke Kasino Neon Mirage seperti orang yang punya misi—dan $10.000 membakar kantongnya. Udara berdengung penuh harap, lampu-lampu berkelap-kelip seperti sirene takdir. Dia di sini bukan untuk poker atau roulette. Tidak, malam ini, ia hanya mengincar satu mesin: The Billionaire's Bounty, mesin slot baru yang dikabarkan memiliki glitch... yang bisa menghasilkan jackpot $1 miliar.

Ia menemukannya di sudut terjauh, setengah tertutup bayangan. Tak ada antrean, tak ada gembar-gembor—hanya layar yang berkedip-kedip dan dengungan aneh, seolah tahu ia akan datang.

Brettski duduk, memasukkan seratus yang tajam, dan menarik tuas.

Putaran pertama: Ceri. Batang. Tengkorak.
Putaran kedua: Batang. Ceri. Tengkorak.
Putaran ketiga: Tengkorak. Tengkorak. Tengkorak.

Layarnya glitch—kode biner berkedip sebentar—sebelum kembali normal. Pembayarannya? $0.

Ia menertawakannya, tetapi menyadari sesuatu yang aneh: jamnya berdetak mundur.

Ia terus bermain. $100 demi $100. Waktu terasa kabur—orang-orang bergerak lebih lambat, minuman tetap penuh, udara terasa lebih pekat. Pada putaran ke-49, ia mendapatkan tiga berlian. Mesin itu mengerang dan mengeluarkan token emas.

"Masukkan untuk membuka Fase Dua," bisik layar.

Ia ragu sejenak. Lalu memasukkannya.

Tiba-tiba, mesin itu terbelah, memperlihatkan layar kedua... yang lebih mirip antarmuka satelit daripada permainan. Koordinat berkelebat. Simbol dalam bahasa yang tak dikenalnya bergulir cepat.

Keamanan mulai mendekat. Lampu merah menyala. Mesin itu berbicara lagi:

"Diperlukan autentikasi jackpot. Letakkan telapak tangan di pemindai."

Brettski mengulurkan tangan—lalu berhenti. Telapak tangannya memiliki tanda aneh, bersinar redup.

Dan kemudian lantai kasino mulai bergemuruh.

Layar berkedip menampilkan satu pesan terakhir:

"Hanya satu pemain yang boleh mengklaim takhta."

Dan lantai di bawahnya runtuh.

Bersambung.

it.title: Ho provato una nuovissima slot machine!
it.description:
Sto regalando 50.000 $ che NON vorrai perderti!: http://codebrettski.com

Siamo TORNATI al Casinò... a giocare a una slot machine NUOVISSIMA! Vediamo come va, mi aspetto ALMENO 3 pagamenti manuali... se non 7. Grazie mille a tutti per aver messo "Mi piace", per esservi iscritti e per aver lasciato i vostri pensieri nei commenti. Anche se mi state prendendo in giro, vi amo comunque. Siete tutti bellissimi e apprezzo davvero ognuno di voi per avermi accompagnato in questo folle viaggio. Auguratemi buona fortuna e ci vediamo alla prossima! Andiamo in guerra.

Brettski entrò a grandi passi al Neon Mirage Casino come un uomo con una missione, con 10.000 $ che gli bruciavano in tasca. L'aria vibrava di attesa, le luci lampeggiavano come sirene del destino. Non era lì per il poker o la roulette. No, quella sera aveva occhi solo per una macchina: The Billionaire's Bounty, una nuovissima slot machine che si diceva avesse un problema tecnico... un problema che avrebbe potuto far uscire il jackpot da un miliardo di dollari.

La trovò nell'angolo più lontano, semi-nascosta nell'ombra. Nessuna coda, nessuna fanfara: solo uno schermo tremolante e uno strano ronzio, come se sapesse che stava arrivando.

Brettski si sedette, inseriva un centinaio di dollari e tirava la leva.

Primo giro: Ciliegia. Bar. Teschio.
Secondo giro: Bar. Ciliegia. Teschio.
Terzo giro: Teschio. Teschio. Teschio.

Wir sind WIEDER im Casino … und spielen an einem brandneuen Spielautomaten! Mal sehen, wie es läuft. Ich rechne mit mindestens 3 Handauszahlungen … wenn nicht sogar 7. Vielen Dank an alle fürs Liken, Abonnieren und eure Kommentare. Auch wenn ihr mich aufzieht – ich liebe euch trotzdem. Ihr seid alle wunderbar, und ich bin jedem einzelnen von euch wirklich dankbar, dass ihr mich auf dieser verrückten Reise begleitet habt. Wünscht mir Glück, wir sehen uns beim nächsten Mal! Auf in den Krieg!

Brettski betrat das Neon Mirage Casino wie ein Mann mit einer Mission – und 10.000 $, die ihm in der Tasche brannten. Die Luft summte vor Vorfreude, Lichter blinkten wie Sirenen des Schicksals. Er war nicht zum Pokern oder Roulette hier. Nein, heute Abend hatte er nur ein Auge auf einen einzigen Automaten geworfen: The Billionaire's Bounty, einen brandneuen Spielautomaten, dem Gerüchten zufolge ein Fehler auftrat ... einer, der den 1-Milliarden-Dollar-Jackpot ausschütten könnte.

Er fand ihn in der hintersten Ecke, halb im Schatten. Keine Schlange, kein Getöse – nur ein flackernder Bildschirm und ein seltsames Summen, als hätte er gewusst, dass er kam.

Brettski setzte sich, warf einen frischen Hunderter ein und zog den Hebel.

Drehung eins: Kirsche. Bar. Totenkopf.
Drehung zwei: Bar. Kirsche. Totenkopf.
Drehung drei: Totenkopf. Totenkopf. Totenkopf.

Der Bildschirm hatte einen Fehler – kurz blitzte ein Binärcode auf –, bevor er wieder normal angezeigt wurde. Die Auszahlung? 0 Dollar.

Er lachte darüber, bemerkte aber etwas Seltsames: Seine Uhr tickte rückwärts.

Er spielte weiter. 100 Dollar nach 100 Dollar. Die Zeit selbst schien zu verschwimmen – die Leute bewegten sich langsamer, die Getränke blieben voll, die Luft dicker. Bei Drehung 49 traf er drei Karos. Die Maschine stöhnte und schoss einen Goldchip aus.

„Einstecken, um Phase Zwei freizuschalten“, flüsterte der Bildschirm.

Er zögerte. Dann steckte er ihn ein.

Plötzlich öffnete sich die Maschine und gab einen zweiten Bildschirm frei … einen, der eher wie eine Satellitenschnittstelle als wie ein Spiel aussah. Koordinaten blinkten. Symbole in einer ihm unbekannten Sprache liefen schnell durch die Luft.

Die Sicherheitskontrolle näherte sich. Rote Lichter flackerten auf. Die Maschine sprach erneut:

„Jackpot-Authentifizierung erforderlich. Handfläche auf den Scanner legen.“

Brettski streckte die Hand aus – und hielt inne. Auf seiner Handfläche war ein seltsamer Fleck, der schwach leuchtete.

Und dann begann der Casinoboden zu beben.

Auf dem Bildschirm flackerte eine letzte Nachricht:

„Nur ein Spieler kann den Thron besteigen.“

Und der Boden gab unter ihm nach.

Fortsetzung folgt.

es-US.title: ¡Probé una máquina tragamonedas completamente nueva!
es-US.description:
¡Estoy regalando $50,000 que no te querrás perder!: http://codebrettski.com

¡Estamos de vuelta en el Casino… Jugando en una tragamonedas NUEVA! A ver qué tal resulta. Espero al menos 3 pagos manuales… si no 7. Muchas gracias a todos por darle a "me gusta", suscribirse y dejar sus comentarios. Aunque me estén tomando el pelo, los sigo queriendo. Son todos preciosos, y de verdad agradezco a cada uno de ustedes por acompañarme en este viaje tan loco. ¡Deséenme suerte y nos vemos en la próxima! ¡Vamos a la guerra!

Brettski entró al Casino Neon Mirage como un hombre con una misión, y $10,000 quemándole el bolsillo. El aire vibraba de anticipación, las luces destellaban como sirenas del destino. No había venido para jugar al póker ni a la ruleta. No, esta noche, solo tenía los ojos puestos en una máquina: La Recompensa del Multimillonario, una tragamonedas flamante de la que se rumoreaba que tenía un fallo... uno que podría desembolsar el premio mayor de mil millones de dólares.

La encontró en el rincón más alejado, medio envuelta en sombras. Sin cola, sin fanfarria, solo una pantalla parpadeante y un zumbido extraño, como si supiera que venía.

Brettski se sentó, metió cien billetes y tiró de la palanca.

Giro uno: Cereza. Barra. Calavera.
Giro dos: Barra. Cereza. Calavera.
Giro tres: Calavera. Calavera. Calavera.

La pantalla falló —parpadeando brevemente un código binario— antes de volver a la normalidad. ¿El premio? Cero dólares.

Se rió, pero notó algo extraño: su reloj iba al revés.

Siguió jugando. Cien dólares tras cien dólares. El tiempo mismo parecía difuminarse: la gente se movía más despacio, las bebidas seguían llenas, el aire se espesaba. En el giro 49, sacó tres diamantes. La máquina gimió y disparó una ficha dorada.

"Inserta para desbloquear la Fase Dos", susurró la pantalla.

Dudó. Luego la insertó.

De repente, la máquina se abrió, revelando una segunda pantalla… una que parecía más una interfaz de satélite que un juego. Las coordenadas parpadearon. Símbolos en un idioma que no reconocía se desplazaban rápidamente.

El personal de seguridad comenzó a acercarse. Las luces rojas se encendieron. La máquina volvió a hablar:

"Se requiere autenticación para el bote. Coloque la palma de la mano en el escáner".

Brettski extendió la mano, pero se detuvo. Su palma tenía una extraña marca, brillando tenuemente.

Y entonces, la sala del casino comenzó a temblar.

La pantalla mostró un último mensaje:

"Solo un jugador puede reclamar el trono".

Y la sala cedió bajo sus pies.

Continuará.

ko.title: 새로운 슬롯머신을 테스트해봤어요!
ko.description:
5만 달러를 드립니다! 놓치지 마세요!: http://codebrettski.com

카지노로 돌아왔습니다... 새 슬롯머신을 플레이하고 있어요! 어떻게 될지 두고 봅시다. 최소 3번은... 아니, 7번은 될 것 같아요. 좋아요와 구독, 그리고 댓글로 생각을 남겨주셔서 정말 감사합니다. 저를 욕하시더라도, 저는 여전히 여러분을 사랑합니다. 여러분 모두 아름다우시고, 이 미친 여정에 함께해 주신 모든 분들께 진심으로 감사드립니다. 행운을 빌어주시고, 다음 여정에서 만나요! 자, 전쟁터로 나갑시다.

브렛스키는 마치 사명감을 가진 사람처럼 네온 미라지 카지노로 성큼성큼 걸어 들어갔습니다. 주머니에 구멍이 뚫린 1만 달러가 불타고 있었죠. 기대감으로 가득했고, 불빛은 운명의 사이렌처럼 번쩍였습니다. 그는 포커나 룰렛을 하러 온 게 아니었습니다. 아니, 오늘 밤, 그의 눈은 오직 한 대의 기계에만 집중되어 있었다. 바로 '억만장자의 현상금', 결함이 있다는 소문이 돌았던 새 슬롯머신이었다. 10억 달러 잭팟이 터질 수도 있는 기계였다.

그는 구석에서 그림자에 반쯤 가려진 기계를 발견했다. 줄도, 팡파르도 없었다. 그저 깜빡이는 화면과 그가 오는 것을 알고 있는 듯한 이상한 윙윙거리는 소리만 들릴 뿐이었다.

브렛스키는 자리에 앉아 빳빳한 100달러를 넣고 레버를 당겼다.

첫 번째 스핀: 체리. 바. 스컬.
두 번째 스핀: 바. 체리. 스컬.
세 번째 스핀: 스컬. 스컬. 스컬.

화면에 잠깐 이진 코드가 깜빡이다가 정상으로 돌아왔다. 배당률은? 0달러였다.

그는 웃어넘겼지만, 이상한 점을 발견했다. 시계가 거꾸로 돌아가고 있었다.

그는 계속 게임을 했다. 100달러가 100달러씩. 시간 자체가 흐릿해지는 듯했다. 사람들은 더 느리게 움직이고, 술잔은 가득 차 있었고, 공기는 ​​더 짙어졌다. 49번째 스핀에서 그는 다이아몬드 세 개를 맞췄다. 기계가 으르렁거리며 금화 하나를 쏘아 올렸다.

"2단계 잠금 해제를 위해 넣으세요." 화면이 속삭였다.

그는 망설였다. 그리고 그것을 넣었다.

갑자기 기계가 갈라지며 두 번째 화면이 나타났다. 게임이라기보다는 위성 인터페이스처럼 보였다. 좌표가 깜빡였다. 그가 알아들을 수 없는 언어로 된 기호들이 빠르게 스크롤되었다.

보안 요원이 다가왔다. 빨간 불이 켜졌다. 기계가 다시 말했다.

"잭팟 인증이 필요합니다. 스캐너에 손바닥을 대세요."

브렛스키는 손을 뻗었다가 멈췄다. 그의 손바닥에는 희미하게 빛나는 이상한 자국이 있었다.

그리고 카지노 바닥이 덜컹거리기 시작했다.

화면에 마지막 메시지가 깜빡였다.

"단 한 명의 플레이어만 왕좌를 차지할 수 있습니다."

그리고 그의 발밑에서 바닥이 무너졌다.

계속된다.

#슬롯 #블랙잭 #도박 #카지노 #바카라 #룰렛

브렛스키는 누구인가? 브렛스키는 베가스 맷, 블러프, 데겐달트, 미스터 핸드 페이, 레이디 럭 HQ 등 고대 전설들과 같은 프로 도박꾼입니다! 하지만 이러한 전설들과는 달리, 브렛스키는 슬롯머신, 룰렛, 블랙잭, 크랩스, 버블 크랩스, 포커, 바카라 등 수천 년 동안 장로들이 축적해 온 고대 지식을 보유하고 있습니다. 프로 도박꾼으로서 브렛스키의 목표는 간단합니다. 도박으로 번 돈을 이용해 라스베이거스를 완전히 장악하는 것입니다. 그의 세계 정복 여정을 응원하려면 구독하세요.

ja.title: 最新のスロットマシンをテストしました！
ja.description:
5万ドルをプレゼント！絶対に見逃せない！: http://codebrettski.com

カジノに戻ってきました… 最新スロットマシンでプレイ中！ どうなるか見てみましょう。少なくとも3回は…いや、7回は…と予想しています。いいね！やチャンネル登録、コメント欄へのご意見など、本当にありがとうございます。たとえ私を批判しても、私は皆さんのことが大好きです。皆さんは素晴らしいです。このクレイジーな旅路を共に歩んでくれた一人一人に、心から感謝しています。幸運を祈ってください。次回もお会いしましょう！さあ、戦いましょう。

ブレツキーは、使命を帯びた男のように、そしてポケットに1万ドルを燃やしながら、ネオンミラージュカジノに闊歩しました。期待に満ちた空気が渦巻き、運命のサイレンのようにライトが点滅していました。彼はポーカーやルーレットをするためにここに来たのではありません。いや、今夜、彼の目当てはたった一つのマシンだった。「ビリオネアズ・バウンティ」。噂によると、不具合があるらしい真新しいスロットマシンで…なんと10億ドルのジャックポットが飛び出すかもしれないというのだ。

彼は奥の隅で、半分影に覆われたそのマシンを見つけた。行列もファンファーレもなく、ただ画面がチラチラと点滅し、奇妙なブーンという音がするだけだった。まるで彼が来ることを知っているかのようだった。

ブレツキーは椅子に座り、100ドルを投入し、レバーを引いた。

1回転目：チェリー。バー。スカル。
2回転目：バー。チェリー。スカル。
3回転目：スカル。スカル。スカル。

画面に不具合が起こり、バイナリコードが一瞬点滅したが、すぐに正常に戻った。配当は？0ドル。

彼は笑い飛ばしたが、奇妙なことに気づいた。時計が逆回転しているのだ。

彼はプレイを続けた。100ドル、100ドル。時間そのものがぼやけていくようだった。人々の動きは鈍くなり、飲み物は満杯のまま、空気は重苦しくなった。49回目のスピンで、彼はダイヤモンドを3つ揃えた。マシンがうなり声をあげ、金のトークンを発射した。

「フェーズ2を解除するにはトークンを挿入してください」と画面が囁いた。

彼はためらい、それからトークンを挿入した。

突然、マシンが割れ、2つ目のスクリーンが現れた…それはゲームというより、衛星インターフェースのようだった。座標が点滅し、彼の知らない言語の記号が高速でスクロールした。

警備員が近づき始めた。赤いライトが点滅した。マシンは再び音声を発した。

「ジャックポットの認証が必要です。スキャナーに手のひらを当ててください。」

ブレツキーは手を伸ばしたが、すぐに止まった。彼の手のひらには奇妙な跡が、かすかに光っていた。

そして、カジノのフロアが揺れ始めた。

スクリーンに最後のメッセージがちらついた。

「王座を狙えるのは、たった一人のプレイヤーだけです。」

そして、彼の足元で床が崩れ落ちた。

続く。

#スロット #ブラックジャック #ギャンブル #カジノ #バカラ #ルーレット

Brettskiとは？Brettskiは、ベガス・マット、ブラフ、デゲン・ダルト、ミスター・ハンド・ペイ、レディ・ラックHQといった伝説のプレイヤーたちと肩を並べるプロギャンブラーです。しかし、これらの伝説のプレイヤーとは異なり、Brettskiはスロットマシン、ルーレット、ブラックジャック、クラップス、バブルクラップス、ポーカー、バカラといったスキルにおいて、長老たちから受け継いだ数千年にわたる古代の知識を蓄積しています。プロギャンブラーとしてのBrettskiの目標はシンプルです。ギャンブルで稼いだ資金を使って、ラスベガスを制覇することです。彼の世界制覇への旅を応援するために、チャンネル登録をお願いします。

snippet.title: Every GTA 5 SECRET Scene (No One Saw Them All)
snippet.description:
I decided to explore what happens if you always switch characters after completing missions in GTA 5. Rockstar created dozens of unique scenes where Michael, Franklin, or Trevor comment on the events that just happened, but many players never see them. Some of these hidden cutscenes make sense, while others are broken or tied to cut content. Going through the story chronologically, I showcase these rare moments, strange inconsistencies, and overlooked details that reveal how GTA 5 was built.

Roblox is an online platform and game creation system where users can play games, socialize, and create their own games. It provides a user-friendly environment for developers to design games using the Roblox Studio, a powerful game development tool that employs the Lua programming language for scripting. Games on Roblox are hosted on the platform and can range across various genres, including adventure, role-playing, simulations, racing, and more.

Roblox is available on a variety of platforms, making it accessible to a wide audience. It can be played on Windows and macOS through the dedicated desktop apps, as well as on iPhones and iPads via the Roblox app in the App Store. Android users can access it through the Google Play Store, and Xbox One users can enjoy the platform through a dedicated app available in the Microsoft Store. Additionally, the Roblox website allows for account management, game browsing, and launching games.

snippet.title: Ash & Iron is a Complete Disaster for Destiny 2...
snippet.description:
Talking about the absolute disaster that is the Ash & Iron "Major Update" Launch. The Destiny 2 Community is NOT HAPPY right now. An underwhelming Activity shoved into the portal, A Confusing Event, time-gated content, and Eververse Price increases. It's not going very well for Destiny 2.
--FOLLOW ME ON TWITCH: www.twitch.tv/kackishd

--- My Twitter: https://twitter.com/RickKackis

New #destiny2 video, going over the Ash & Iron Update Launch. We have new "Reclaim" Activity, New Territories Event, and the new Ash and Iron Rewards Pass (Ash and Iron Season Pass) in Season: Reclamation after the Destiny 2 News in the Latest TWAB (This week at Bungie) or TWID (This Week in Destiny) for September 4th, during Destiny 2: The Edge of Fate! The New Edge of Fate DLC Launch is Here! We have the New Year of Prophecy and Season: Renewal (Season of Renewal) that have gone live! We have a New Edge of Fate Campaign, and Kepler, the new Edge of Fate Destination! There are many Kepler Secrets to uncover! We also have the New Sieve Activity! And we have Armor 3.0, Destiny 2 Stats Overhaul, and the New Destiny 2 Portal! All leading to the New Destiny 2: Renegades Star Wars DLC!
The Ash and Iron Major Update is here! We return to the Plaguelands Location! We have new Legendary Weapons, and fan favorites like the MIDA Mini-Tool and Dreng! We also have New Exotic Weapons and a New Exotic Quest!
But today we're going over the new Ash and Iron Update, and the outrage within the Destiny 2 Community it has caused.
 #destiny2news #destiny2edgeoffate

snippet.title: Testing Scary Minecraft Myths Caught On Camera...
snippet.description:
Buy NEW MERCH now, including the CHECKPOINT COMIC and G.U.I.D.O PLUSHIE!:
https://checkpointmerch.com

Check out the CHECKPOINT WEBSITE and make YOUR OWN Character!: https://checkpointmultiverse.com/

Today in the Minecraft Dimension, Steve and G.U.I.D.O from Checkpoint are CATCHING SCARY MYTHS on camera. Seve must explore multiple stories from his friends to investigate and catch Scary Myths! Can Steve find all SCARY MYTHS and catch them on camera? This is I Caught Minecraft Scary Myths on Camera...
__

👋🏼 Checkpoint Website: https://checkpointmultiverse.com/
📸 Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/checkpoint.yt
❤️ Connect With Us: https://direct.me/checkpointmultiverse
🧑🏼‍🤝‍🧑🏼 Join the Community on Discord: https://discord.gg/jkfV7mSxB6

🎵 Additional Music provided by Epidemic Sound: https://www.epidemicsound.com/

MORE CHECKPOINT ADVENTURES:

‣ MINECRAFT DIMENSION: https://bit.ly/3mKfUOL


¬

Minecraft is an open world game that has no specific goals for the player to accomplish, allowing players a large amount of freedom in choosing how to play the game however, there is an achievement system. The gameplay by default is first person, but players have the option to play in third person mode. The core gameplay revolves around breaking and placing blocks. The game world is essentially composed of rough 3D objects—mainly cubes—that are arranged in a fixed grid pattern and represent different materials, such as dirt, stone, various ores, water, and tree trunks. While players can move freely across the world, objects and items can only be placed at fixed locations relative to the grid. Players can gather these material blocks and place them elsewhere, thus allowing for various constructions.

#Checkpoint #Minecraft

Free and out in the wild, you continue your quest for revenge. But the Baron still has his hooks in you; his experiments wreaking havoc, the zombie DNA clashes with yours and it seems to be winning. You’re losing control…When it takes over, your strength is pushed beyond human limits. But your devastating beastly powers won’t be enough once the night comes and the true horrors emerge…

Unleash the Beast – September 19! PRE-ORDER NOW 👉https://go.dyinglight.com/pre-order-now


Facebook: https://facebook.com/dyinglightgame
Twitter: https://twitter.com/dyinglightgame
Instagram: https://instagram.com/dyinglightgame
